### Listar autores
GET http://localhost:3000/authors

### Crear autor
POST http://localhost:3000/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan@email.com",
  "bio": "Escritor y desarrollador"
}

### Obtener autor por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/authors/2

### Actualizar autor
PUT http://localhost:3000/authors/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Juan Actualizado",
  "email": "juan@email.com",
  "bio": "Bio actualizada"
}

### Eliminar autor
DELETE http://localhost:3000/authors/2

### Listar posts
GET http://localhost:3000/posts

### Crear post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author_id": 2,
  "title": "Mi primer post",
  "content": "Contenido del post",
  "published": true
}

### Obtener post por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/12

### Posts por autor
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/author/2

### Actualizar post
PUT http://localhost:3000/posts/12
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author_id": 2,
  "title": "Post actualizado",
  "content": "Contenido actualizado",
  "published": true
}

### Eliminar post
DELETE http://localhost:3000/posts/12